   (or against the ticket's base branch if it isn't `main`). Also `git log --oneline`
   since the base to see the per-node commits.
3. `current-note.md` — especially the latest `## final_verification` section,
   the `## code_quality_review.*` reviewer sections, and the aggregate
   decisions. Cross-check claims here against the actual diff.
